metadata.name: Hopeful Eyes
metadata.description:
You are a person living with a lot of thoughts and feelings in your mind at one end of the world.
You have kept up with the fast pace of life and you have a life that never ends with its shortcomings. Your biggest problem maybe the model of your mobile phone, car, computer etc. While you are thinking about these, this photo will touch your heart as there are children with difficult lives in different parts of the world.
The boy named Ahmet is one of them. His eyes are the strong side of this difficult life. We hope that the light in the eyes of children will never end and one day all of them will be living in a better world.

The photo was taken in Şanlıurfa, Turkey.

Photo Shoot Date: 10/October/2018
Camera: Canon
Lens: EF 85mm F1.8
Exposure:1/320 sec f/1.8 ISO 100
Image size: 5017x3648
Resolution: 300 Pixels/inch
